setParent

public RhizosphereMetaModel.Attribute setParent(boolean isParent)
Marks this attribute as establishing a parent-child relationship between visualization models. If set, the values Rhizosphere models will have for this attribute must point to the unique id of the parent model (see RhizosphereModelAttribute.modelId()).

When parent-child relationships exist within visualization models, Rhizosphere can offer advanced layout operations (such as hierarchical treemaps) that leverage this information.

Parameters:
isParent - Whether this attribute establishes a parent-child relationship.
Returns:
the Attribute itself, for chaining.
